room_title: Escape room "Neverland" by Once Upon An Escape in Las Vegas
room_description:
Voyages ahead! A dream this is not!
You must be on the lookout to not get caught!

With a dash of pixie dust, soar through the London sky! Sneak up on Captain Hook’s ship and venture into the seemingly enchanting world of Neverland. But once there, you’ll need to save Wendy from the Lost Boys’ unruly grip! The clock is ticking. Outwit the crocodile and make your escape from the place where you never have to grow up!
